Package com.neebal.android.simplyreliable.exception

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    BadResponseException
    Represents an exception that will be thrown if the response sent by the server is not in the required json format.
    CreateMultipartGetMsgFileException
    Exception that will be thrown if unable to create a file on the local client device, at the time of downloading the multipart file from the server
    GetMessageResponseFileStorageException
    Represents an exception that will be thrown if there was some error with regards to the file in which the response of the get data is stored.
    InputStreamReadException
    Custom exception that will be thrown if there is any error at the time of reading from the input stream.
    PersistableMessageReadFailedException
    Exception object that will be thrown if there is any error in reading a PersistableMessage instance from the data store.
